<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="love-vt">love <strong><em>vt</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /lʌv/    美 /lʌv/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>[不用于进行时] 爱；热爱</strong></h4>
<p>反 hate： </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I love my motherland deeply.
我深深地热爱我的祖国。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They love each other.
他们彼此相爱。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>爱好；喜爱</strong></h4>
<p>反 hate </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We love sports. 
我们喜爱体育活动。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>love doing / to do sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I love going out to restaurants. 
我喜欢下馆子。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They love to travel / traveling.
他们喜欢旅游。</p><footer>2013湖北</footer></div>

<h4 id="3-wouldd-love">3.★ <strong>[常与would连用，口语中略作’d love] 想；愿意：</strong></h4>
<ul>
<li>would love (sb/sth) to do sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I’d love to have a part-time job. 
我想做一份兼职工作。</p><footer>北师大⑤ – 13</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I'd love you to come with me.
我想让你跟我一起去。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>lover /'lʌvə(r)/ n [C]  </p></div>